                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8718" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SCLM-0210</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2118 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东风如何破浪：红海危局下的供应链安全之困</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How does Dongfeng Break the Waves: the Dilemma of Supply Chain Security in the Dangerous Situation of the Red Sea</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘凯，李静怡，吴雨佳，陈嘉怡，李自鹏，孙嘉阳</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中南财经政法大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国东风汽车工业进出口有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">运输部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">供应链安全；国际物流管理；国际运输实践；东风集团；2024百优案例；微案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">supply chain security; international logistics management; international transportation practice; Dongfeng Group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">提高供应链韧性与安全是打造世界级企业的关键环节。由于红海危机，全球主要航运公司暂停红海航线运输，东风集团的整车物流受到了极大的影响。本案例基于东风集团提升供应链韧性目标，以东风如何缓解红海危机所带来的运力短缺问题为主线，讲述了东风通过绕航好望角、与国际海运公司签订长期合约和变更运输港口等方式，敏捷应对供应链中断问题的故事。案例再现了东风集团在面对突发危机时解决整车运输问题的真实过程，让学生深入理解供应链安全及韧性的重要性，学会分析供应链环境、识别关键因素以及制定短期和长期供应链战略的方法，培养学生快速响应并处理复杂情景下的问题解决能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Improving the resilience and safety of the supply chain is a key concern for Chinese automobile companies at present. Due to the Red Sea crisis, major shipping companies around the world have suspended transportation on the Red Sea route, and the vehicle logistics of Dongfeng Group has been greatly affected. This case is based on the goal of improving the resilience of the supply chain of Dongfeng Group, and focuses on how Dongfeng Group can alleviate the shortage of transportation capacity caused by the Red Sea crisis. It tells the story of how Dongfeng Group agilely responded to the disruption of the supply chain by detouring around the Cape of Good Hope, signing long-term contracts with international shipping companies, and changing transportation ports. The case reproduces the real process of Dongfeng Group in solving vehicle transportation problems in the face of sudden crises, allowing students to understand and apply knowledge points related to supply chain security, international logistics management, and transportation decision-making practices in supply chain management, and guiding students to think about how to solve supply chain transportation problems from a practical perspective.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《供应链物流管理》、《供应链管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">供应链安全；国际物流管理；供应链韧性与危机预防；供应链可持续发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-10</td>
                            </tr>
